== Integrating Data Sources ==

External data sources such as relational databases, CSV files, Excel spreadsheets, XML files or JSON can be easily integrated into the {{PRODUCT}}.

A three-step process assists the integration of external data sources:
# [[Help:DataSources | Configure a data source]] to read external data.
# [[Help:DataSourceMappings | Specify a mapping]] to transform the data into RDF and fit your ontologies.
# [[Help:DataOpsPostProcessing | optionally add post-processing]] to improve the linking with existing data.

This process can also create a [[Help:Providers | data provider]] that automatically updates external data on a periodic basis.

To get started, [[Help:DataSources | create a data source]].


